    'featured_listings.HowLongWillMyListingAppearInFeaturedListings_content': 'A kiemelt hirdet\xE9sek id\u0151tartam\xE1t hetekben m\xE9rj\xFCk (7 nap). Hirdet\xE9seit legfeljebb 4 h\xE9tre emelheti ki.',
